{"id":232888881,"title":"推 給沒自信在意他人眼光的你我","content":"活在這個世界\n多多少少我們都受過不友善的對待\n但有多少人能真正不在意那些流言蜚語\n\n《我決定 我是誰》\n淺顯易懂的文字\n偶爾犀利令人莞爾\n咀嚼其中他—鍾明軒—透過自己的親身經歷來告訴我們如何獨自去面對這個世界\n人生來就是孤獨的走的時候也是孤獨的\n因此我們都要學會勇敢去面對\n\n這本書給我的感觸不深不淺剛剛好\n其實我不算他的粉絲但一直都很欣賞\n我喜歡他的漂亮、自信、勇敢、活出自我\n看完書也才知道他也是自己一路慢慢成長\n自己去釋懷很多事\n我也常因為他人的話語感到在意\n但我就是我啊 我就是這樣所以是我\n從來不應該活在別人口中\n要學著好好愛自己\n成就更好的自己\nhttps://i.imgur.com/8BWjfLI.jpg","excerpt":"活在這個世界，多多少少我們都受過不友善的對待，但有多少人能真正不在意那些流言蜚語，《我決定 我是誰》淺顯易懂的文字，偶爾犀利令人莞爾，咀嚼其中他—鍾明軒—透過自己的親身經歷來告訴我們如何獨自去面對這個","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"e0a290f4-752b-48a2-a791-f211f8b46588","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-14T07:48:24.204Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T07:48:24.204Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":16,"tags":[],"topics":["我決定我是誰"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"書籍","forumAlias":"book","school":"胖胖男友vs蠢蠢女友","department":"d5487","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":16}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/8BWjfLI.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"f2f50b12-1647-4d41-a733-a6cb7a9d78b5","url":"https://i.imgur.com/8BWjfLIl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/8BWjfLIl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/8BWjfLIl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-14T07:48:24.204Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T07:48:24.204Z"},{"id":"f2f50b12-1647-4d41-a733-a6cb7a9d78b5","url":"https://i.imgur.com/8BWjfLI.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/8BWjfLI","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/8BWjfLIl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-14T07:48:24.204Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T07:48:24.204Z"}],"postAvatar":""}